Package cz.vse.java.authentication

Interface IAuthenticationScenario

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FingerPrintDBAuthenticator, IPDBAuthenticator, TokenValidator, UserAuthenticator
    public interface IAuthenticationScenario

    The interface of IAuthenticationScenario is used to contain all methods of the type to be overriden (implemented).

    Instances implementing this interface are used for providing authentication at many levels for the various IConnections. Mostly are used in combination with AuthenticationHandlerContainer.

    Written for project "Connections2".
    Version:
    03. 04. 2020 .vse.java.authentication
    Author:
    Vojtěch Pavlů
    See Also:
